full_threads.body:
Summary of Responsibilities:

1. Bug Fixes & Integration

  • Fix Flodesk Data Mapping: Investigate why the "First Name" and "Last Name" fields are currently blank for new subscribers and inquiries.
    • Reference: Jillian provided a screenshot of how it should look based on older data.

2. Performance Optimization

  • Mobile Speed Test: Investigate mobile load times, as Jillian specifically noted slowness on her mobile device.
  • Performance Benchmarking: Gather current site metrics and compile a comparison against the old website's performance metrics.

3. Analytics & Reporting

  • Hotjar Analysis: Review Hotjar data (heatmaps/recordings) to analyze user behavior on the new site and prepare a summary of insights.

action.text: Allie Borcena assigned to Adriane Roa

Hi all,

Thank you for getting the website up and running! I have noticed one thing in our automation for the newsletter and contact form to flodesk- it doesn't seem to be capturing the first name and last name information that is being entered. Here is a screenshot of an older subscriber so you can see how the information used to come through. Right now everything from first name and last name is blank for new subscribers and enquiries.



I also wanted to check in on the latest load speed? I noticed it was a bit slow to load for me the other day, but do we have some metrics versus the old site?
I'd also love any analysis you have on how the new website is going from Hotjar?

Thanks so much- looking forward to working with you all!
Kind Regards,

JILLIAN DINKEL
